{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-issues-tsx","path":"/issues/15","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"repo":"https://github.com/lencx/dev"}},"issuesJson":{"id":"a1313401-9cf8-54e5-a057-48116e56022c","title":"父容器高度不固定，内部元素怎样才可以滚动？","number":15,"bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\">当滚动内容高度小于 300px 时，父容器高度等于滚动容器高度；当滚动容器高度大于 300px 时，滚动容器应该滚动，但是以下实现未滚动，应该如何解决？</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://codepen.io/lencx/pen/XWzLjPP\" rel=\"nofollow\">CodePen Demo</a></p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".parent {\n  max-height: 300px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.scroll {\n  overflow-y: auto;\n}\"><pre>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">parent</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">max-height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">300<span class=\"pl-smi\">px</span></span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">overflow</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> hidden;\n}\n\n.<span class=\"pl-c1\">scroll</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">overflow-y</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> auto;\n}</pre></div>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-text-html-basic notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"&lt;div class=&quot;parent&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;div class=&quot;scroll&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;!-- &lt;p&gt; text 1 &lt;/p&gt; --&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt; text .. &lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;!-- &lt;p&gt; text n &lt;/p&gt; --&gt;\n  &lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\"><pre><span class=\"pl-kos\">&lt;</span><span class=\"pl-ent\">div</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">class</span>=\"<span class=\"pl-s\">parent</span>\"<span class=\"pl-kos\">&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"pl-kos\">&lt;</span><span class=\"pl-ent\">div</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">class</span>=\"<span class=\"pl-s\">scroll</span>\"<span class=\"pl-kos\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"pl-c\">&lt;!-- &lt;p&gt; text 1 &lt;/p&gt; --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"pl-kos\">&lt;</span><span class=\"pl-ent\">p</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">&gt;</span> text .. <span class=\"pl-kos\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"pl-ent\">p</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"pl-c\">&lt;!-- &lt;p&gt; text n &lt;/p&gt; --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"pl-kos\">&lt;</span><span class=\"pl-ent\">div</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"pl-kos\">&lt;</span><span class=\"pl-ent\">div</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">&gt;</span></pre></div>","updatedAt":"2022-06-27T09:49:19Z","upvoteCount":1,"author":{"login":"lencx","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16164244?u=77d1d01930d8e36105a49a6c474abf70eeee74b1&v=4","url":"https://github.com/lencx"},"category":{"isAnswerable":false,"name":"Web","emoji":":globe_with_meridians:"},"labels":{"edges":[{"node":{"name":"CSS","color":"563d7c"}},{"node":{"name":"Interview","color":"662E4E"}}]},"comments":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"DC_kwDOG2u5tM4AI3C2","bodyHTML":"<p dir=\"auto\">解决方案，只需修改 parent 的 css 即可。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p dir=\"auto\">在弹性布局模型中，弹性容器的子元素可以在任何方向上排布，也可以“弹性伸缩”其尺寸，既可以增加尺寸以填满未使用的空间，也可以收缩尺寸以避免父元素溢出。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-css notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\".parent {\n  max-height: 300px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n}\"><pre>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">parent</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">max-height</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">300<span class=\"pl-smi\">px</span></span>;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">overflow</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> hidden;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">display</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> flex;\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">flex-direction</span><span class=\"pl-kos\">:</span> column;\n}</pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">参考资源</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout\" rel=\"nofollow\">CSS Flexible Box Layout</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/boxes-fill-height-dont-squish/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Boxes That Fill Height (Or More) (and Don’t Squish)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/22914399/flexbox-misbehaving-with-max-height\" rel=\"nofollow\">flexbox misbehaving with max-height</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@stephenbunch/how-to-make-a-scrollable-container-with-dynamic-height-using-flexbox-5914a26ae336\" rel=\"nofollow\">How to make a scrollable container with dynamic height using Flexbox</a></li>\n</ul>","author":{"login":"lencx","avatarUrl":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16164244?u=77d1d01930d8e36105a49a6c474abf70eeee74b1&v=4","url":"https://github.com/lencx"},"replies":{"edges":[]}}}]}}},"pageContext":{"number":15,"previous":{"title":"Web 缓存","number":5},"next":{"title":"JS 深拷贝与浅拷贝","number":14}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3993188973"]}